{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"jQuery","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/jQuery","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>jQuery</strong> 是一个着重简化 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/DOM\">DOM</a> 操作，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/AJAX\">AJAX</a> 调用和<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/event\">事件 <small>(en-US)</small></a>处理的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\">库</a>。一些前端 JavaScript 开发者经常会用到它。</p>\n<p>jQuery 使用 <code>$(selector).action()</code> 的格式给一个（或多个）元素绑定事件。具体来说，<code>$(selector)</code> 让 jQuery 选择匹配 CSS 选择器 <code>selector</code> 的元素，并将它/它们传递给叫做 <code>.action()</code> 的事件 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/API\">API</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ready</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#blackBox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">hide</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>上述代码和以下代码功能相同：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World!\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"blackBox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>display <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"none\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"下载_jquery","title":"下载 jQuery","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>npm</th>\n      <th>bower（单文件）</th>\n      <th>Google CDN</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>npm install jquery</code></td>\n      <td><code>bower install https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.min.js</code></td>\n      <td><code>https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js</code></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"更多学习","title":"更多学习","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知识","title":"基本知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>维基百科上的 <a title=\"jQuery\" href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/JQuery\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">jQuery</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://jquery.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">jQuery 官方网站</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术信息","title":"技术信息","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://api.jquery.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">官方 API 文档</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"下载 jQuery","id":"下载_jquery"},{"text":"更多学习","id":"更多学习"}],"summary":"jQuery 是一个着重简化 DOM 操作，AJAX 调用和事件 (en-US)处理的 JavaScript 库。一些前端 JavaScript 开发者经常会用到它。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"jQuery","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/jquery","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/jquery/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/jQuery","title":"jQuery"}],"pageTitle":"jQuery - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}